{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"70b38197fa","title":"中央办公厅关于向军队调查材料办法的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7bca3a2f8f","index":0,"year":1969,"month":8,"day":6,"articleId":"70b38197fa","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"71d63b8b5f","name":"中央办公厅"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ef3831e978","type":"title","text":"中央办公厅关于向军队调查材料办法的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed50809a13","type":"paragraph","text":"中发[1969]49号","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f1a139ed6","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区、县革命委员会，各总部，各军种、兵种，各大军区、省军区，各军、师、团：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f25e9ef279","type":"paragraph","text":"各单位在清理阶级队伍中，大量派人到部队调查材料，对保守部队番号、部署等军事机密极为不利。遵照伟大领袖毛主席关于“保守党的机密，慎之又慎”和“节约闹革命”的教导，各单位向军队调查材料的办法需加以改进。为此，特作如下规定：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8c0a4c4000","type":"paragraph","text":"一、向军队调查材料，原则上应采取函调办法。即由调查单位写好调查提纲，寄至省军区或大军区，由军区政治机关转有关单位和人员。如所查单位不在本军区，则转有关军区、军种、兵种和有关总部查告。材料写好后，由所在团以上政治机关直接转给调查单位。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9613ef1316","type":"paragraph","text":"二、在特殊情况下，必须派人到部队调查时，仍由县以上革命委员会批准，经省军区和军以上政治机关核准后，方可去部队调查，但须从严控制。对保密单位，海防、边防部队，重要设防地区以及刚调防的部队不得去人调查。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3f5b6e864","type":"paragraph","text":"三、各单位应加强保密教育，不得泄露军事机密。军事单位凡有代号的一律使用代号。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d66811db34","type":"paragraph","text":"四、军队各机关、部队，对来调函件必须认真及时处理。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"98757e44e4","type":"paragraph","text":"上述通知，请认真贯彻执行。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e801d93b53","type":"paragraph","text":" \t中共中央办公厅","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52d2671c0d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六九年八月六日","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cdc863e98d","type":"paragraph","text":"已发：各省、市、自治区、县革命委员会，各总部，各军种、兵种，各大军区、省军区，各军、师、团。共印四二、四二三份。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"982621ad64","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央办公厅 一九六九年八月七日发出","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8e277af62","type":"paragraph","text":"（根据中央文件原件打印）","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0850c5780b","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据中央文件原件打印","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"70b38197fa","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}